quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  77,1,By those sent one after another
  77,2,"then the violent winds, blowing violently"
  77,3,"and those that scatter, scattering"
  77,4,"then those that distinguish, distinguishing (right from wrong)"
  77,5,then those that bring down the reminder
  77,6,excusing or warning
  77,7,That which you are promised will certainly befall
  77,8,So when the stars are made to disappear
  77,9,and when the sky is cleft asunder
  77,10,and when the mountains are uprooted as dust
  77,11,and when the messengers are brought (at their) appointed time
  77,12,For which day (is this) timed
  77,13,For the day of decision
  77,14,"And what will make you realize, what the day of decision is"
  77,15,"Sorrowful will be the state on that day, of the deniers"
  77,16,Did We not destroy the ancients
  77,17,Then We made the others to follow them
  77,18,Thus do We deal with the criminals
  77,19,"Sorrowful will be the state on that day, of the deniers"
  77,20,Did We not create you from a fluid (which is) weakened after vigor
  77,21,Then We made it to stay in a place
  77,22,till (the fulfilment of) the known programme
  77,23,"thus We programmed, for We are Excellent Programmers"
  77,24,"Sorrowful will be the state on that day, of the deniers"
  77,25,"Did We not make the earth, one that draws together to itself"
  77,26,the living and the dead (due to the force of its gravity)
  77,27,And We made therein lofty ranges of mountains and gave you to drink sweet water
  77,28,"Sorrowful will be the state on that day, of the deniers"
  77,29,"(It will be said to them), “Proceed towards that which you used to deny"
  77,30,Proceed towards the covering having three branches
  77,31,neither (giving) cool shade nor making one free from the flame
  77,32,it certainly throws sparks like palaces
  77,33,as if they were yellow camels.”
  77,34,"Sorrowful will be the state on that day, of the deniers"
  77,35,This is the day (on which) they will not speak
  77,36,And permission will not be given to them that they may put forth excuses
  77,37,"Sorrowful will be the state on that day, of the deniers"
  77,38,"This is the day of decision, We have gathered you and the ancients"
  77,39,"So if there is any plot you have, then do plot against Me"
  77,40,"Sorrowful will be the state on that day, of the deniers"